      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",

      "offset_seconds": 119,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,

      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",

      "duration_seconds": 2,

      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "That's rough.",

      "offset_seconds": 128,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So... Well, I guess there's not much we can do about that but...",

      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",

      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",

      "offset_seconds": 145,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 6,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
